          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Nippon and US Steel sue to save merger</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/ls-jan-7-1.jpg" alt="Nippon and US Steel sue to save merger" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Nippon Steel and US Steel filed <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-07-01-2025-h1-1-multiple-lawsuits" target="_blank">multiple lawsuits</a> to salvage their blocked merger. President Biden halted the deal, citing national security concerns. However, the companies claim the decision was politically motivated. They’ve filed lawsuits against Cleveland-Cliffs and the United Steelworkers alleging anticompetitive practices. Trump criticized the merger, calling for US Steel to thrive under tariffs. Though litigation is underway, experts say reversing Biden's decision will be tough.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
